content.rendered:
BOSS AIR AIRBAG 2503 COMPLETE

Boss Air Airbag 2503 Complete available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This product has a 2500lb or 1136kg capacity @ 100psi Government approved, tested to over 750psi. Suitable for “Bag over” applications and as a stand alone air bag in Automotive suspension.

Includes:

  • 2500lb Extreme Series triple Bag
  • Top and Bottom plate and stainless bolts.
  • 12 countersunk stainless bolts

Fully Compressed – 85mm with 6mm ends fitted
Max Diameter- 155mm (widest when fully compressed)
Max height – 335mm
Max working pressure 0-160psi
Test pressure – 480psi
Burst pressure – 1000psi

To view the full range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!

For more 4×4 inspiration follow us on Instagram and Facebook
